<Layout title="好圈圈好感形象學苑 - 形象打底，好感無敵">

	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-500 to-secondary-500 text-white py-20 relative">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
			<h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-6">好圈圈，你的好感形象教練</h1>
			<p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-2xl mb-6 sm:mb-8">形象打底，好感無敵</p>
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm sm:text-lg mb-6 sm:mb-8">好圈圈好感形象學苑專注於協助魅力菁英的職場人士，在職場和生活中從內而外發揮最大的影響力和好感力。</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="/services" class="inline-block bg-white text-pink-600 font-semibold px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base sm:text-lg">了解我們的服務</a>
